Package: openFDA
Title: 'openFDA' API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Parker", , "simon.parker.24@ucl.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-8214-4496"))
Description: The openFDA API facilitates access to Federal Drug Agency (FDA)
  data on drugs, devices, foodstuffs, tobacco, and more. This package makes the
  API easily accessible, returning objects which the user can parse into JSON
  data. More information on the openFDA API is available at
  <https://open.fda.gov/about/>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
